OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775927152
OL,3,CPolice investigating cyber attack on
OL,4,CNI school IT systems
OL,6,FThe police has confirmed it is
OL,7,Finvestigating what it has described as
OL,8,Fa 'potential network intrusion' on
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland's school IT system
OL,10,Fknown as C2K.
OL,12,FIt is a week on from the cyber attack
OL,13,Fwith some teachers and students forced
OL,14,Fto return to the classroom over the
OL,15,FEaster holidays to reconnect to the
OL,16,Fsystem.
OL,18,FIt provides all online and IT for
OL,19,Fschools across Northern Ireland and is
OL,20,Fmanaged by the Education Authority.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775927152
OL,3,CPolice investigating cyber attack on
OL,4,CNI school IT systems
OL,6,FIn a statement the PSNI told UTV they
OL,7,Fwere made aware of a 'potential
OL,8,Fnetwork intrusion within a public
OL,9,Fservice organisation on Thursday, 2nd
OL,10,FApril.'
OL,12,FIt continued: "The matter has been
OL,13,Freferred to specialist detectives in
OL,14,Fthe Police Service of Northern
OL,15,FIreland's Cyber Crime Investigation
OL,16,FTeam, who are investigating the matter.
OL,18,F"It would be inappropriate to make any
OL,19,Ffurther comment at this time."
OL,26,@tD@OOUzD@AOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775927152
OL,3,CPolice investigating cyber attack on
OL,4,CNI school IT systems
OL,6,FThe office of the information
OL,7,Fcommissioner also said in a statement
OL,8,Fthey had been made aware of an
OL,9,Fincident by the Education Authority
OL,10,Fand are assessing the information
OL,11,Fprovided.
OL,13,FTeaching unions met with the EA
OL,14,Fearlier on Friday as the new school
OL,15,Fterm is due to resume on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775927152
OL,3,CPolice investigating cyber attack on
OL,4,CNI school IT systems
OL,6,FThey described the meeting as
OL,7,F'constructive' and told UTV they are
OL,8,Fso far content with assurances around
OL,9,Fpupil and teacher data not being
OL,10,Fleaked but they will continue to
OL,11,Fmonitor the situation.
OL,13,FThe Education Authority which manages
OL,14,Fthe network has previously said there
OL,15,Fis so far no evidence that teacher or
OL,16,Fpupil data has been compromised.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
